                    <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Executing strategy | Using pattern libraries | Pushing hard | Getting fast feedback.</p>
                    <p>Think elite athletes at their best: they aren't doing anything fundamentally new in competition. They're deploying existing skills and patterns under pressure with maximum efficiency.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="pt-4 border-t border-white/10">
                    <p class="text-[9px] md:text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest text-zinc-500 uppercase">
