            <p class="text-zinc-400">Where exactly your system is leaking and how exactly it's affecting your decisions and thinking process.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 border-l-2 border-zinc-700 bg-black/20 rounded-r-2xl">
            <p class="text-zinc-300 italic leading-relaxed">
              "You can map it alone. I did. It took five months at rock bottom to see what I can show someone else in one conversation. <span class="text-white font-medium">That's the only difference. Not capability. Time and cost.</span>"
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-white/5">
            <p class="text-white font-bold mb-6 text-lg">In one conversation, we will:</p>
